						               													<description>Let's PLAAY Tennis is a &amp;ldquo;pro tennis toolbox&amp;rdquo; that includes several components, allowing you to dial in to the level of detail you desire. If quick play is what you&amp;rsquo;re looking for, the Tournament Mode module will let you simulate the early and middle rounds of an entire tournament in about 20 minutes, reducing the field to a handful of finalists. You can then use the &amp;ldquo;For The Set&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;No Rally&amp;rdquo; modules to resolve the remaining tournament matches in 10 to 20 minutes more.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On the other hand, if you&amp;rsquo;re looking for detail, the &amp;ldquo;point-by-point&amp;rdquo; module will let you watch the action unfold as if you were courtside, with serves, returns, difficult shots, winners, momentum and even unusual and rare results.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The &amp;ldquo;For the Set&amp;rdquo; module is the main tool in the box. It serves as a bridge between the two extremes of speed and detail. It will instantly resolve the preliminary action of a set and take you to the potential set-deciding game--one player with the opportunity to win the sixth and deciding game of the set. From there, you can get to your final result with extended drama, point-by-point, or instantly via the &amp;ldquo;No Rally&amp;rdquo; results.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
